  "descriptions": [
    {
      "description": "This is a generic template to allow scientists in using a well structured data workflow following the project-oriented approach and findable accessible interoperable and reusable (FAIR) principles for data and code publication in science. The project contains a example of data from the CIMMYT market intelligence research (Donovan et al 2025, https://doi.org/10.1017/S001447972500002X) with data description and an example of R script for analysis and documentation. Feel free to delete the example files once the project is adapted for your needs.",
      "descriptionType": "Abstract"
    }
